Z6jTvauYSsu\",\"snapshot\":\"c14f5bcbb08c9ab23735d6640e040bfcc95b7f34\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n{\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1784314287110,\"sessionID\":\"ses_08e99c9b8ffeUnNZ6jTvauYSsu\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f716b45e20013Myq5bBvBPW5ha\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f716b2fac001MB2T3v01nQ2hRG\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_08e99c9b8ffeUnNZ6jTvauYSsu\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"## Iteration 1 Complete\\n\\n- **Status:** `complete`\\n- **Findings:** 4 new\\n- **newInfoRatio:** `1.0`\\n- **Key result:** Replay records named defaults as telemetry but still defers with `workflowMode:null`.\\n- **Next focus:** Runnable named-vs-null live benchmark matrix.\\n- **Verification:** 3 artifacts valid; canonical records match; citations `4/4`; exactly one state record appended.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1784314283490,\"end\":1784314287109},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"msg_0afabbb8c184a109016a5a79ab685c81918e61754abbc5dbbe\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}}}}\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1784314287465,\"sessionID\":\"ses_08e99c9b8ffeUnNZ6jTvauYSsu\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f716b5567001lahLBPig54EUgW\",\"reason\":\"stop\",\"snapshot\":\"1d4ab799160462f316dc2295247c65fbacebdab6\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f716b2fac001MB2T3v01nQ2hRG\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_08e99c9b8ffeUnNZ6jTvauYSsu\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":114700,\"input\":1427,\"output\":100,\"reasoning\":21,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":113152}},\"cost\":0}}\n","exit":0,"truncated":true,"outputPath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/.local/share/opencode/tool-output/tool_f7166e1f10010QKlu77vx4eSu5"},"title":"PROMPT=$(<\".opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/021-default-mode-policy-research/research/lineages/sol-ultra/prompts/iteration-1.md\") && MK_SPEC_GATE_ENFORCE=0 AI_SESSION_CHILD=1 opencode run --model openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast --format json --auto --pure --dir \"$PWD\" \"Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not