{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784314952122,"sessionID":"ses_08ea082c9ffe7l0Exu0UkBOne2","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_iz7diqoAqjpTeCVT531W0EI5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0063-skilled-router-collapse/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/021-default-mode-policy-research/research/lineages/sol-ultra/deep-research-state.jsonl"},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0063-skilled-router-collapse/.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/021-default-mode-policy-research/research/lineages/sol-ultra/deep-research-state.jsonl</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\"type\":\"config\",\"topic\":\"Parent-hub defaultMode policy, run 2: a divergent multi-model deep dive over the Divergent Exploration Agenda in the packet spec.md.\",\"maxIterations\":3,\"minIterations\":3,\"convergenceThreshold\":0.05,\"stopPolicy\":\"max-iterations\",\"antiConvergence\":{\"convergenceMode\":\"default\",\"stopPolicy\":\"max-iterations\",\"divergent\":{}},\"resource_map_present\":false,\"resource_map\":{\"emit\":true},\"createdAt\":\"2026-07-17T18:42:58.447Z\",\"specFolder\":\".opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/021-default-mode-policy-research\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-sol-ultra-1784313510669-wn3vsj\",\"generation\":1,\"nextRunAt\":null,\"remainingDelayMs\":null}\n2: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":1,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\",\"run\":1,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Contrarian and live-routing pass: steelman named defaults, inspect actual replay/default semantics, and identify evidence that could falsify the run-1 recommendation.\",\"findingsCount\":4,\"newInfoRatio\":1.0,\"noveltyJustification\":\"All four findings are new to this lineage: configuration telemetry was separated from selected behavior, the bounded named-default case was established, contradictory gold semantics were exposed, and a paired live falsification experiment was defined.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"What is the strongest evidence-backed case that named defaults remain preferable, and where does the run-1 verdict overreach?\",\"How should null fallback resources, Layer-0/Layer-1 interaction, and live-model behavior be experimentally evaluated?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"What is the strongest evidence-backed case that named defaults remain preferable, and where does the run-1 verdict overreach?\"],\"ruledOut\":[\"Treating routeTelemetry.defaultApplied as evidence that replay selected the default child\",\"Using deterministic replay alone to settle live-model behavior\"],\"toolsUsed\":[\"Read\",\"Grep\",\"Glob\",\"Bash\"],\"sourcesQueried\":[\".opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/router-replay.cjs\",\".opencode/skills/sk-prompt/mode-registry.json\",\".opencode/skills/sk-prompt/manual_testing_playbook/hub_routing/ambiguous_default.md\",\".opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/manual_testing_playbook/hub_routing/ambiguous_defer.md\",\".opencode/skills/mcp-tooling/manual_testing_playbook/hub_routing/ambiguous_defer.md\",\".opencode/commands/deep/skill-benchmark.md\"],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-17T18:48:03Z\",\"durationMs\":305000,\"graphEvents\":[]}\n3: {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":2,\"mode\":\"research\",\"target_agent\":\"@deep-research\",\"agent_definition_loaded\":true,\"resolved_route\":\"Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not_switch_mode=true\",\"execution\":\"single_iteration\",\"state_source\":\"externalized_files\",\"do_not_switch_mode\":true,\"run\":2,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Specify the paired live experiment as a runnable benchmark matrix: corpus construction, named-vers